oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Open side helicopter block product model, circa 1964
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Product model of an open side helicopter block used in the 1964 catalog for Sherman and Reilly, Inc., of Chattanooga, Tennessee. Text on the cover reads, "Open sided block allows the conductor to be dropped directly into the sheave without having to unlatch the block-frame."
